title: Week 4 Studs & Duds + Panic Alarms, Monday Punday - Fantasy Football Podcast for 10/4
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason discuss the biggest Studs & Duds of Week 4! Get a recap of the week-winning performances, and the soul-crushing ones too. Plus, Monday Punday and NFL injury updates. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for October 4th, 2021.
